title: DDFP 392: Week 4 review & Quarter Season Awards
itunes:title: DDFP 392: Week 4 review & Quarter Season Awards
description:
Shek is joined by Dan Hanzus and Marc Sessler to discuss Monday Night Football, and make their selections for the "Quarter Season Awards." Later Ike Taylor and Maurice Jones-Drew join the show to recap the biggest stories from Week 4, as well as the art of trash talking. 

Learn more about your ad-choices at https://www.iheartpodcastnetwork.com
